Get access to DelftBlue: https://doc.dhpc.tudelft.nl/delftblue/Accounting-and-shares/
Use EduVPN to access DelftBlue. Login on OpenOndemand in your browser: https://login.delftblue.tudelft.nl/. 
Copy the "simulation_files" from the pipeline to your open ondemand. 
Open DelftBlue in your terminal and go to the folder of perovskite you want to use. 
type "sbatch run.sh" to submit your job.
Use squeue to check the queue
Submit more jobs if needed.
When finished, you can start analyzing the data. 
